title: #92Noon! VikingsTalkers/Gleeman/Russo
description: First half of the show is dedicated mostly to the Vikings and looking forward to 2021. Gleeman joins, but big Wild news of the day takes over the final hour, and Russo joins to expand on his breaking report.
